eses, free-range eggs, in-house prosciutto ham, and zero-kilometer sourced meat. Every Monday evening, Sull\\u2019Albero hosts a <strong>gourmet Farmers' Market<\\\/strong> where guests can choose from a range of fresh meat, fish, cheese, and seasonal produce on offer, watch it being cooked on the spot, and dine outdoors in a convivial atmosphere of live music.<\\\/p>\",\"content_column_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"icon_width\":80,\"image_align\":\"top\",\"image_grid_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"image_grid_width\":\"1-2\",\"image_svg_color\":\"emphasis\",\"link_style\":\"default\",\"link_text\":\"Read more\",\"margin\":\"default\",\"meta_align\":\"below-title\",\"meta_element\":\"div\",\"meta_style\":\"text-meta\",\"title\":\"La Trattoria sull'Albero\",\"title_align\":\"top\",\"title_element\":\"h2\",\"title_grid_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"title_grid_width\":\"1-2\",\"title_hover_style\":\"reset\",\"title_style\":\"h3\"}},{\"type\":\"button\",\"props\":{\"grid_column_gap\":\"small\",\"grid_row_gap\":\"small\",\"margin\":\"default\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"button_item\",\"props\":{\"button_style\":\"default\",\"content\":\"More about la Trattoria\",\"dialog_layout\":\"modal\",\"dialog_offcanvas_flip\":true,\"icon_align\":\"left\",\"link\":\"food-and-wine\\\/trattoria-sullalbero-restaurant\\\/\"}}]}]},{\"type\":\"column\",\"props\":{\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"padding\":\"small\",\"position_sticky_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"width_large\":\"2-3\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"slideshow\",\"props\":{\"class\":\"inbox-slider\",\"link_style\":\"default\",\"link_text\":\"Read more\",\"margin\":\"remove-vertical\",\"margin_remove_bottom\":true,\"margin_remove_top\":true,\"meta_align\":\"below-title\",\"meta_element\":\"div\",\"meta_style\":\"text-meta\",\"nav\":\"\",\"nav_align\":\"center\",\"nav_breakpoint\":\"s\",\"nav_position\":\"bottom-center\",\"nav_position_margin\":\"medium\",\"overlay_animation\":\"parallax\",\"overlay_position\":\"center-left\",\"show_content\":true,\"show_link\":